{"tid":530901,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[Harry Potter] 佛地魔：傳人的起源","createTime":"2018-01-16T08:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T17:45:24.000Z","uid":130563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"709df97d7ba1b3db557217ab6e6b82897ec678e0","tid":530901,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T08:51:12.000Z","msg":"《佛地魔：傳人的起源》（英語：Voldemort: Origins of the Heir）是一部於2018年發佈的意大利奇幻冒險電影，由粉絲製作，為非官方的《哈利波特》系列電影前傳。該片由吉恩瑪麗亞&middot;皮薩陀（Gianmaria Pezzato）與史帝方諾&middot;普拉斯迪亞（Stefano Prestia）執導，透過發起募資活動籌措製片經費。Tryangle Films擔任該片的製片商。<br />\n<br />\n2016年7月，握有《哈利波特》系列電影版權的華納兄弟以侵犯版權為由提起訴訟，募資活動被迫中止。後來，雙方達成和解，前提是《佛地魔：傳人的起源》不得成為一部具營利性質的電影。該片的首支預告片於2017年6月釋出，而最終預告則於12月發佈。《佛地魔：傳人的起源》將於2018年1月13日在YouTube上發佈。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有興趣？睇完傾下計。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C6SZa5U8sIg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DC6SZa5U8sIg&d=5lQWy1R1WVXVkzQq1%2B40NQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a16955e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C6SZa5U8sIg</a>"},{"pid":"d008ecb14025e60477387b016c5ed627aabfe99a","tid":530901,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T08:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d792226dd783388b898cdc4673686fe160a58a53","tid":530901,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:25:24.000Z","msg":"如果哈迷可以睇下，冇BUG但故事一般演員演技又..."},{"pid":"0f809b25b40a089a40036e836888fd7ed425622c","tid":530901,"uid":19727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d792226dd783388b898cdc4673686fe160a58a53","tid":530901,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:25:24.000Z","msg":"如果哈迷可以睇下，冇BUG但故事一般演員演技又..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T13:25:04.000Z","msg":"睇下無壞，之前有套講GGAD既短片都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gi